<p>I've been on this Wiki for several years and I love SCP-999 with my entire heart. You can state your own preferences for the wiki, but state them as *your own preferences*. If you're going to try to speak for the other members, you need to actually ASK some other members first. You can't just assume everyone shares your opinion and claim your own feelings are the popular sentiment.</p>

							</div>

								
					
